Master of Shadows
One of the important figures of the invasion of Gipath will be a sorcerer called the Master of Shadows. He can summon shadows and control them. This sorcerer must be killed.
#subobj  1
Entering the city
The Master of Shadows lives in a rich town house. To find it, you must first enter the city. 
#subobj  2
Finding the Master's estate
You will know the Master of Shadows' estate by the gates that are decorated by two giant figures of eagles sitting on turtles.
#subobj  3
Opening the gates
To enter the estate, get the gates open first.
#subobj  4
Finding the Master of Shadows
The Master of Shadows is somewhere on the estate.
#subobj  5
Killing the Master of Shadows
The Master of Shadows must be killed.